{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey","slug":"daily-141-the-community-survey","title":"The Community Survey","title_ko":"마을 설문조사","level":"B1","ageBand":"10-12","coverUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/cover.webp","summary_ko":"Jun과 Mina는 마을 사람들의 의견을 모아 설문조사를 완성하고, 반 친구들 앞에서 결과를 발표한다.","wordCount":316,"stage":6,"collection":"daily","pages":[{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Ms. Park handed a survey sheet to each student.","translation_ko":"박 선생님이 학생들에게 설문지를 한 장씩 나눠 주었다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Ms","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"Park","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":440,"endMs":660},{"word":"handed","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":660,"endMs":980},{"word":"a","charStart":16,"charEnd":17,"startMs":980,"endMs":1200},{"word":"survey","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1420},{"word":"sheet","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1780},{"word":"to","charStart":31,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1780,"endMs":1940},{"word":"each","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2220},{"word":"student","charStart":39,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2560}]},{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"We are learning about our community,\" she said.","translation_ko":"\"우리 마을에 대해 알아볼 거예요,\" 선생님이 말했다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"We","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"are","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":460},{"word":"learning","charStart":8,"charEnd":16,"startMs":460,"endMs":800},{"word":"about","charStart":17,"charEnd":22,"startMs":800,"endMs":1140},{"word":"our","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1320},{"word":"community","charStart":27,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1320,"endMs":2140},{"word":"she","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2260},{"word":"said","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2500}]},{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p1-s3","ord":2,"text":"\"Ask neighbors what they need most.\"","translation_ko":"\"이웃에게 마을에서 가장 필요한 것을 물어보세요.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/audio/p1-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Ask","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"neighbors","charStart":5,"charEnd":14,"startMs":420,"endMs":860},{"word":"what","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":860,"endMs":1140},{"word":"they","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1360},{"word":"need","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1660},{"word":"most","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2040}]}]},{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun read the sheet carefully.","translation_ko":"준은 설문지를 꼼꼼히 읽었다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"read","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":480,"endMs":780},{"word":"the","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":780,"endMs":1000},{"word":"sheet","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1200},{"word":"carefully","charStart":19,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1700}]},{"id":"daily-141-the-community-survey-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"It listed five choices: a park, a library, a sports center, a garden, or a recycling station.","translation_ko":"공원, 도서관, 스포츠 센터, 텃밭, 재활용 센터, 이렇게 다섯 가지가 적혀 있었다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-141-the-community-survey/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":30,"endMs":237},{"word":"listed","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":237,"endMs":597},{"word":"five",